Logged in just the up vote Riot taking the time to put rude people in their places anyways,{{summoner:11}} ed

SO with Illaoi how did you guys come to the decision to put her spawned tentacles on walls? Was it a thematic thing where is makes more sense for them to be summoned out of the environment, or is it a balance thing where if tentacles spawned in the ground in lane it could cause a problem with her being a very strong lane bully? I am very curious to know how you guys came to this decision. 

Best regards- Pixil77{{sticker:slayer-pantheon-thumbs}}
